        {
            "id": 6009063,
            "title": "3,000多輛汽車海上起火 貨船包租方：客戶訊息不便公布",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>一艘從中國港口出發載有 3,000 多輛汽車的滾裝船在太平洋上起火，近日引發關注。經船東方 Zodiac Maritime 公司確認，「Morning Midas」輪上全部 22 名船員無人傷亡，已經棄船，並被安全轉移。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009063%2Fl%2F544291b3130049027d319a1c8e98dfd3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">一艘從中國港口出發載有3,000多輛汽車的滾裝船在太平洋上起火，近日引發關注。（圖：Shutterstock）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《每日經濟新聞》周四（5 日）報導，經確認，上汽安吉物流股份有限公司為「Morning Midas」輪的包租方，負責貨物配載計畫，船舶的船員配備和營運管理則由船東方負責。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>「目前我們在等待船東的消息，業務團隊也在同步核實相關訊息。」安吉物流董秘表示，若獲得確切訊息，會進一步對外公布。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>安吉物流相關工作人員介紹，此前安吉物流從未發生過類似汽車運輸船起火事件。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，由於事故原因尚不清楚，且船舶事故理賠流程複雜，涉及事故調查、損失評估及責任認定等環節，因此，預計耗時會較長。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>與此同時，基於客戶訊息保密原則，本次事件涉及的承運車輛數量、型號以及所屬企業訊息暫不便對外公布。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
